text: Sonia Bouloukbachi (born 10 January 1996) is a French water polo player. She was a member of the France women's national water polo team at the 2015 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * sonia- bouloukbachi * water-polo-match-reports-day-1 * fina women Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:French water polo players
